Come visit us at:

7128 Miramar Rd. Suite 10 (Upstairs) San Diego, CA 92121. 

We're in the same shopping plaza as Tony's Mexican Restaurant, just West of the Pyramid.

Phone #: (858) 247-0953

18+: a valid Government-Issued Photo ID W/ a CA Medical Marijuana Recommendation
